#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.__init__:7 of
msgid ""
"传入 :meth:`AgentConfig.from_kwargs` 的扁平参数（节选）：  - "
"``max_tool_rounds``：单步最大工具轮数（默认 24） - ``preload_workspace_paths``：预读文件列表（注入 "
"system prompt 的 workspace 快照） - ``thread_key_state_paths``：thread 压缩时附带的 "
"KEY_STATE_JSON 文件路径列表 - ``system_prompt_max_identity_chars``：Agent Identity "
"JSON 总长度上限（默认 10000） - ``workspace_read_chunk_chars``：``workspace_read`` / "
"``read_skill`` 单段最大字符数（默认 32000，允许 1024–96000） - "
"``tool_result_thread_budget_chars``：单条 TOOL_RESULT_JSON 序列化预算（默认 65536） - "
"``profile_max_chars`` / ``profile_truncate_chars``：profile 写入 Identity "
"前的截断上限（默认 4000） - ``bash_retries`` / ``bash_timeout_retries``：bash "
"超时后的额外重试次数（写入 ``LoopConfig.bash_retries``，默认 1，即共 2 次执行） - "
"``llm_transient_retries``：thread 压缩等直连 ``acompletion`` 遇瞬时错误时的最大重试次数（默认 2） -"
" ``tool_decision_max_retries``：传给 ``acompletion_with_pydantic_validation`` 的"
" max_retries（默认 10） - ``model`` / ``llm_model``：LiteLLM 路由模型名（用于 "
"token_counter 与 tiktoken 回退） - ``tiktoken_encoding``：强制指定 tiktoken 编码名（默认 "
"``cl100k_base``）"
msgstr ""
"Pass in the flattened parameters of :meth:`AgentConfig.from_kwargs` "
"(excerpt): - ``max_tool_rounds``: Maximum number of tool rounds in a single "
"step (default 24) - ``preload_workspace_paths``: Pre-read file list "
"(workspace snapshot injected into system prompt) - "
"``thread_key_state_paths``: KEY_STATE_JSON file path list that comes with "
"thread compression - ``system_prompt_max_identity_chars``: Agent Identity "
"JSON Total length limit (default 10000) - ``workspace_read_chunk_chars``: "
"``workspace_read`` / ``read_skill`` Maximum number of characters in a single"
" paragraph (default 32000, 1024–96000 allowed) - "
"``tool_result_thread_budget_chars``: Single TOOL_RESULT_JSON serialization "
"budget (default 65536) - ``profile_max_chars`` / ``profile_truncate_chars``:"
" The upper limit of truncation before profile is written to Identity "
"(default 4000) - ``bash_retries`` / ``bash_timeout_retries``: The number of "
"additional retries after bash timeout (write ``LoopConfig.bash_retries``, "
"default 1, that is, a total of 2 executions) - ``llm_transient_retries``: "
"Thread compression and other direct connections ``acompletion`` The maximum "
"number of retries in case of transient errors (default 2) - "
"``tool_decision_max_retries``: max_retries passed to "
"``acompletion_with_pydantic_validation`` (default 10) - ``model`` / "
"``llm_model``: LiteLLM routing model name (used for token_counter and "
"tiktoken fallback) - ``tiktoken_encoding``: Mandatory specification of "
"tiktoken encoding name (default) ``cl100k_base``)"

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.__init__:7 of
msgid "传入 :meth:`AgentConfig.from_kwargs` 的扁平参数（节选）："
msgstr ""
"Passing in the flattened parameters of :meth:`AgentConfig.from_kwargs` "
"(excerpt):"

