msgstr "Dictionary of execution results."

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.step:1 of
msgid "执行一个仿真步并持久化会话状态与回放记录。"
msgstr ""
"Execute a simulation step and persist session state and playback records."

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.step:3 of
msgid ""
"流程： 1. 步数递增，重置技能作用域 2. 刷新可见技能列表 3. 构建上下文快照（预读取文件） 4. 执行工具循环（带超时保护） 5. "
"持久化会话状态和回放记录"
msgstr ""
"Process: 1. Increment the number of steps and reset the skill scope 2. "
"Refresh the visible skill list 3. Build context snapshot (pre-read file) 4. "
"Execute tool loop (with timeout protection) 5. Persist session state and "
"playback record"

#: agentsociety2.agent.person.PersonAgent.step:12 of
msgid ""
"对外可展示的一步结论（``finish``/``done`` 的 summary）；内部工具轨迹写入回放， 不再整串拼接进返回值。无有效发言时为 "
"``[no verbal reply]`` 等占位。"
msgstr ""
"A one-step conclusion that can be displayed externally (summary of "
"``finish``/``done``); the internal tool trajectory is written for playback, "
"and the entire string is no longer spliced ​​into the return value. When "
"there is no valid speech, the seats will be occupied by ``[no verbal "
"reply]`` and so on."

