#: ../../api/agent.rst:29
msgid ""
"``AgentBase`` 只规定智能体必须具备的最小生命周期接口。``PersonAgent`` 在此基础上增加了 "
"workspace、技能目录、工具循环、检查点与上下文压缩等运行时能力。"
msgstr ""
"``AgentBase`` only specifies the minimum life cycle interface that the agent"
" must have. ``PersonAgent`` On this basis, runtime capabilities such as "
"workspace, skill catalog, tool loop, checkpoint and context compression are "
"added."

#: ../../api/agent.rst:31
msgid ""
"如果只是扩展人物行为，优先新增或修改 Agent Skill；只有需要改变智能体生命周期、状态机或外部系统调用方式时，才继承 ``AgentBase``"
" / ``PersonAgent`` 创建新类。技能系统的设计说明见 :doc:`/agent_skills`，API 参考见 "
":doc:`/api/skills`。"
msgstr ""
"如果只是扩展人物行为，优先新增或修改 Agent Skill；只有需要改变智能体生命周期、状态机或外部系统调用方式时，才继承 ``AgentBase``"
" / ``PersonAgent`` 创建新类。 See :doc:`/agent_skills` for the design description"
" of the skill system, and see :doc:`/api/skills` for the API reference."

