msgid ""
"API 端点： - GET  /api/v1/agent-skills/list       — 列出所有 agent skill - POST "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/enable     — 启用 skill（进入可选目录） - POST /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/disable    — 禁用 skill - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/scan       — 扫描 "
"workspace/custom/skills/ 下的自定义 skill - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/import     "
"— 从路径导入 skill 目录 - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/create     — 在线创建新 "
"skill（SKILL.md + 可选脚本） - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/upload     — 上传 zip 包导入 "
"skill - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/reload     — 热重载指定 skill - GET  "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/{name}/info — 获取 SKILL.md 内容 - POST /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/remove     — 移除自定义 skill"
msgstr ""
"API endpoints: - GET /api/v1/agent-skills/list - List all agent skills - "
"POST /api/v1/agent-skills/enable - Enable skill (enter optional directory) -"
" POST /api/v1/agent-skills/disable - Disable skill - POST /api/v1/agent-"
"skills/scan - Scan for custom skills under workspace/custom/skills/ - POST "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/import - Import skill directory from path - POST "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/create - Create new skill online (SKILL.md + optional "
"script) - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/upload - Upload zip package to import "
"skill - POST /api/v1/agent-skills/reload - Hot reload specified skill - GET "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/{name}/info — Get SKILL.md content - POST "
"/api/v1/agent-skills/remove — Remove custom skill"

