"This module provides the base class for environment routing and environment "
"modules."

#: ../../api/env.rst:7
msgid "RouterBase"
msgstr "RouterBase"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase:1 of
msgid "环境路由器抽象基类。"
msgstr "Environment router abstract base class."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase:3 of
msgid ""
"Router 用于协调 agent 与环境模块（:class:`~agentsociety2.env.base.EnvBase`）的交互，职责包括："
msgstr ""
"Router is used to coordinate the interaction between the agent and the "
"environment module (:class:`~agentsociety2.env.base.EnvBase`). Its "
"responsibilities include:"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase:5 of
msgid "聚合并过滤环境工具（函数调用 schema）"
msgstr "Aggregate and filter environment tools (function call schema)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase:6 of
msgid "维护仿真时钟（``self.t``）"
msgstr "Maintain simulation clock (``self.t``)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase:7 of
msgid "提供统一 LLM 调用封装（重试与 token 统计）"
msgstr "Provide unified LLM call encapsulation (retry and token statistics)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase:8 of
msgid "生成 world description（可选，用于 PersonAgent 的提示词）"
msgstr "Generate world description (optional, prompt word for PersonAgent)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.__init__:1
#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.__init__:1
#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.__init__:1
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.__init__:1 of
