msgstr "Create a router instance."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.__init__:3
#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.__init__:3
#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.__init__:3
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.__init__:3 of
msgid "环境模块列表。"
msgstr "List of environment modules."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.__init__:4
#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.__init__:4
#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.__init__:4
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.__init__:4 of
msgid "最大执行步数（由具体 router 实现解释）。"
msgstr ""
"Maximum number of execution steps (interpreted by specific router "
"implementation)."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.__init__:5
#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.__init__:5
#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.__init__:5
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.__init__:5 of
msgid "LLM 调用最大重试次数下限（至少为 1）。"
msgstr ""
"Lower limit on the maximum number of retries for LLM calls (at least 1)."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.__init__:6
#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.__init__:6
#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.__init__:6
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.__init__:6 of
msgid "可选回放写入器；若提供会自动注入到各 env module。"
msgstr ""
"Optional playback writer; if provided, it will be automatically injected "
"into each env module."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.sync_simulation_clock:1 of
msgid "与编排器当前仿真时刻对齐。"
msgstr "Aligned with the current simulation moment of the orchestrator."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.sync_simulation_clock:3 of
msgid ""
"``ask``/codegen 的 InitStage 用 ``self.t`` 写入 ``ctx['current_time']``。 若仅在 "
"``env_router.step`` 末尾才更新 ``self.t``，而 agent 先执行，则整步内时钟落后一步。 任何复制 "
"``AgentSociety.step`` 顺序（先 agent 后 env.step）的代码都应在 agent 开始前调用本方法。"
msgstr ""
"The InitStage of ``ask``/codegen writes ``ctx['current_time']`` with "
"``self.t``. If ``self.t`` is updated only at the end of ``env_router.step``,"
" and the agent is executed first, the clock will be one step behind in the "
"entire step. Any code that replicates the ``AgentSociety.step`` sequence "
"(agent first, then env.step) should call this method before the agent "
"starts."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.ask:1 of
msgid "与环境交互的统一入口（由子类实现具体路由策略）。"
msgstr ""
"A unified entrance to interact with the environment (specific routing "
"strategies are implemented by subclasses)."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.ask:3 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "上下文字典。模板模式下可包含 ``variables``，用于 ``{var}`` 替换。"
msgstr ""
"Context dictionary. Template mode can contain ``variables`` for ``{var}`` "
"replacement."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.ask:4 of
msgid "指令文本。模板模式下会进行变量替换后再执行。"
msgstr ""
"Command text. In template mode, variables will be replaced before execution."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.ask:6 of
msgid "是否启用模板模式。"
msgstr "Whether to enable template mode."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.ask:7 of
msgid "``(ctx, answer)``，其中 ctx 可能被环境更新。"
msgstr "``(ctx, answer)``, where ctx may be updated by the environment."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.init:1 of
msgid "初始化路由器与环境模块。"
msgstr "Initialize router and environment modules."

#: agentsociety2.env.base.EnvBase.init:3
#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.init:3 of
msgid "仿真起始时间。"
msgstr "Simulation start time."

#: agentsociety2.env.base.EnvBase.step:1
#: agentsociety2.env.router_base.RouterBase.step:1 of
