msgstr "Built-in router"

#: ../../api/env.rst:26
msgid "ReActRouter"
msgstr "ReActRouter"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter:1 of
msgid "ReAct模式Router：通过Reasoning-Acting循环，使用function calling直接调用所有模块的所有函数。"
msgstr ""
"ReAct mode Router: Through the Reasoning-Acting loop, use function calling "
"to directly call all functions of all modules."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter:3 of
msgid ""
"工作流程： 1. 收集所有环境模块的工具信息 2. 使用LLM的function calling能力选择并调用工具 3. 执行工具调用，获取结果 4. "
"将结果反馈给LLM，继续下一轮Reasoning-Acting循环 5. 直到LLM判断任务完成或达到最大步数"
msgstr ""
"Workflow: 1. Collect tool information of all environment modules 2. Use "
"LLM's function calling capability to select and call tools 3. Execute tool "
"calls and obtain results 4. Feed back the results to LLM and continue the "
"next Reasoning-Acting cycle 5. Until LLM determines that the task is "
"completed or the maximum number of steps is reached"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.ask:1 of
msgid "使用ReAct模式处理指令。"
msgstr "Use ReAct mode to process instructions."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.ask:3
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.ask:3 of
msgid "上下文字典"
msgstr "context dictionary"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.ask:4
#: agentsociety2.env.router_react.ReActRouter.ask:4 of
msgid "指令字符串"
msgstr "command string"

