msgstr "(ctx, answer) tuple"

#: ../../api/env.rst:34
msgid "PlanExecuteRouter"
msgstr "PlanExecuteRouter"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter:1 of
msgid "Plan-and-Execute模式Router：先制定计划，然后执行计划中的步骤。"
msgstr ""
"Plan-and-Execute mode Router: first make a plan, and then execute the steps "
"in the plan."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter:3 of
msgid ""
"工作流程： 1. 收集所有环境模块的工具信息 2. 第一阶段：使用LLM制定执行计划（不调用工具） 3. 第二阶段：按照计划逐步执行工具调用 4. "
"根据执行结果生成最终答案"
msgstr ""
"Workflow: 1. Collect tool information from all environment modules 2. Phase "
"1: Use LLM to develop an execution plan (without calling tools) 3. Phase 2: "
"Execute tool calls step by step according to the plan 4. Generate the final "
"answer based on the execution results"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.ask:1 of
msgid "使用Plan-and-Execute模式处理指令。"
msgstr "Use Plan-and-Execute mode to process instructions."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_plan_execute.PlanExecuteRouter.ask:6 of
msgid "模板模式（PlanExecuteRouter 不使用，仅为签名兼容）"
msgstr ""
"Template mode (not used by PlanExecuteRouter, only compatible with "
"signatures)"

#: ../../api/env.rst:42
msgid "CodeGenRouter"
msgstr "CodeGenRouter"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter:1 of
msgid "代码生成式Router：通过生成Python代码的方式调用环境模块中的@tool标记的接口。"
msgstr ""
"Code-generating Router: Calls the @tool-marked interface in the environment "
"module by generating Python code."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter:3 of
msgid ""
"工作流程： 1. 收集所有环境模块的工具信息 2. 使用类似 pyi 文件的 Python 代码格式向 LLM 提供环境模块描述和工具信息（含 "
"pydantic BaseModel 与模块类定义） 3. LLM 生成 Python 代码来调用工具 4. 使用 AST 解析检查代码安全性 5. "
"通过 compile 和 exec 执行代码，捕获打印输出 6. 根据执行结果和打印输出生成最终响应"
msgstr ""
"Workflow: 1. Collect tool information of all environment modules 2. Provide "
"environment module description and tool information (including pydantic "
"BaseModel and module class definition) to LLM using a Python code format "
"similar to pyi files 3. LLM generates Python code to call tools 4. Use AST "
"parsing to check code safety 5. Execute code through compile and exec, "
"capture printout 6. Generate final response based on execution results and "
"printout"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:1 of
msgid "使用代码生成方式处理指令。通过管道-过滤器架构执行。"
msgstr ""
"Use code generation to process instructions. Execution via pipe-filter "
"architecture."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:3 of
msgid "上下文字典（在template模式下，应包含'variables'键）"
msgstr ""
"Context dictionary (in template mode, should contain the 'variables' key)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:4 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "指令字符串（在template模式下，为模板指令，包含{variable_name}占位符）"
msgstr ""
"Instruction string (in template mode, it is a template instruction, "
"including {variable_name} placeholder)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.ask:6 of
msgid "是否启用模板模式（启用后使用缓存机制）"
msgstr ""
"Whether to enable template mode (use caching mechanism after enabling)"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.init:1 of
msgid ""
"Initialize the router with the start datetime and generate code using LLM. "
"从本地缓存数据库加载当前 env 类型的缓存集，构建 FAISS 索引。"
msgstr ""
"Initialize the router with the start datetime and generate code using LLM. "
"Load the cache set of the current env type from the local cache database and"
" build the FAISS index."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.step:1 of
msgid ""
"Run forward one step for all simulation modules, then output cache "
"statistics. 每步结束后将本步的统计指标以 JSONL 形式追加写入缓存目录，便于分析缓存带来的性能提升。"
msgstr ""
"Run forward one step for all simulation modules, then output cache "
"statistics. After each step, the statistical indicators of this step are "
"appended to the cache directory in the form of JSONL to facilitate analysis "
"of the performance improvement brought by caching."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.dump:1 of
msgid ""
"Dump router state to a serializable dict, including instruction logs and "
"cache stats."
msgstr ""
"Dump router state to a serializable dict, including instruction logs and "
"cache stats."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.load:1 of
