msgstr "CacheStats object, containing all cache statistics"

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.get_cache_stats_summary:1 of
msgid "获取缓存统计信息的摘要字符串。"
msgstr "Get a summary string of cache statistics."

#: agentsociety2.env.router_codegen.CodeGenRouter.get_cache_stats_summary:3 of
